{"article_id":"9yjEClGrRmxq1uUr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Attorney General nominee William P. Barr promised senators Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that he would refuse to carry out orders","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to fire special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and defended the ongoing investigation into Trump campaign figures and Russian election meddling ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"as he sought to assuage concerns","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that he would be President Trump ' s hatchet man .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Barr said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he wouldn ' t be \" bullied \" into bad decisions","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and promised","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that the public would see some transparency from the lengthy investigation","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"- though not necessarily Mr. Mueller ' s full report .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"He rejected Democrats ' suggestions","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that he automatically recuse himself from overseeing the investigation ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"he would make those decisions","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"after weighing all the considerations .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"\" I am not going to do anything","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that I think","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"is wrong ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"and I will not be bullied into doing anything","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"is wrong","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"by anybody , \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" Whether it be editorial boards or Congress or the president ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"I ' m going to do what I think is right . \"","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Mr. Barr ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"who served as attorney general under President George H.W . Bush ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"also weighed in on a host of other weighty issues before the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"he would look into the FBI ' s decision in 2017","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to open an investigation","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"into whether Mr. Trump was secretly working on behalf of Russian interests .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"he wouldn ' t target marijuana companies in states","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"where the drug is legal ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"diverging from Jeff Sessions ' move","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to revoke an Obama-era memo","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"laying out a more relaxed approach .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"he generally favors the sentencing law","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Congress passed late last year ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"also breaking with Mr . Sessions ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"who had urged a tougher line .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"AG nominee William Barr :","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"China , not Russia , is the biggest threat to the U.S .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Mr. Barr also said","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Mr. Trump does have power under the Constitution","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to pardon himself or family members","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"but cautioned","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that there could be political consequences .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" Yes , he does have the power","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to pardon a family member ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"but he would then have to face the fact","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that he could be held accountable for abusing his power , \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Mr. Barr said .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"He generally avoided delving into ongoing legal battles","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"but said","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"he imagines","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"the department would continue to battle for the right","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"to ask a citizenship question on the 2020 census","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"after a judge Tuesday ruled that move illegal .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"he is open to defending the Affordable Care Act in a major court battle underway .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"The department previously said","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"it agreed with states","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that argued","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that most of the law is now unconstitutional .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Barr said","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"he was open to reconsidering that position","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"but wanted to examine it further .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"The Judiciary Committee is holding two days of confirmation hearings for Mr. Barr .","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"On Tuesday , the 20-month-old Mueller investigation dominated the proceedings .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Mr. Barr defended his writing in June of a memo","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"sent to Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"saying Mr. Mueller ' s focus on","depth":16},{"id":77,"text":"whether the president obstructed justice","depth":16},{"id":78,"text":"was \" fatally misconceived. \"","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"He told the Judiciary Committee","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that he wrote it","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"based on press reports .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"Sen. Dianne Feinstein of California , the committee ' s top Democrat , said","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"that raised questions about Mr. Barr ' s \" willingness","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"to reach conclusions","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"before knowing the facts \"","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"and whether he prejudged the Mueller investigation .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Democrats have said","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Mr. Barr should consider recusing himself from overseeing the Mueller investigation","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"as Mr . Sessions did .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Mr. Barr promised to speak with the Justice Department ' s ethics officials","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"but said","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"he would make the final decision .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"his situation is different from that of Mr . Sessions ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"who , as a Trump surrogate , had interactions with the Russian ambassador during the 2016 campaign .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"\" It ' s a judgment call ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"and the attorney general is the person","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"who makes the judgment ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and that ' s what the job entails , \"","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Mr. Barr said .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"When pressed by Sen. Kamala D. Harris , California Democrat , about the scenarios","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"under which he would not follow the ethics officials ' recommendations ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Mr. Barr ' s response was curt .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"He also said","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"he would \" get out as much information","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"as I can \"","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"on Mr. Mueller ' s eventual findings","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"but added","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"that the special counsel ' s report is a prosecutor ' s document","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"that is unlikely to be released in full .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Mr. Rosenstein ,","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"who is overseeing the Mueller investigation","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"but is leaving the Justice Department later this year ,","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"may have reached a conclusion","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"on whether the report will be released .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"Committee Chairman Lindsey Graham , South Carolina Republican , said","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Mr. Barr gave the right answers","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"on publicizing the Mueller report ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"but he doubted","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"it will matter in the end .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"\" The report will be leaked","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"before he gets it , \"","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"the committee chairman predicted .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"Mr. Barr was steadfast in his pledge","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"not to hamper or impede Mr. Mueller .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"he would resist pressure from Mr. Trump","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"to fire the special counsel .","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"\" Under the [ Justice Department ] regulations , Bob Mueller can only be terminated with good cause","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"and , frankly , it is unimaginable to me","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"that Bob would ever do anything","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"that would give rise to good cause , \"","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"\" For me , it would have to be more than that . \"","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Mr. Barr later said","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"he would resign","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"rather than terminate a \" bona fide , lawful investigation into wrongdoing . \"","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"He recounted publicly for the first time efforts","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"to lure him to Mr. Trump ' s legal team","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"and called the overture a \" short-lived \" idea .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Mr. Barr said","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"he was approached in June 2017 by David Friedman , the U.S. ambassador to Israel , about his interest","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"in augmenting Mr. Trump ' s legal team .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"The overture eventually led to a meeting with the president ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"but Mr. Barr declined the offer ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"he \" didn ' t want this burden . \"","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"The meeting ended","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"with Mr. Trump asking for his phone number ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"but Mr. Barr said","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"he never heard back from the president","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"until he asked him to become the nominee for attorney general .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"He recalled telling the president","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"that Mr. Mueller was \" a straight-shooter","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"and could be dealt with as such . \"","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"Mr. Graham said","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"he was happy with the congenial tone of the hearing ,","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"which lacked the kinds of protests","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"that disrupted last year ' s Supreme Court confirmation process .","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":162,"text":"Democrats shouldn ' t penalize Mr. Barr","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"because they disagree with Mr. Trump ' s agenda .","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"\" William Barr had the opportunity today","depth":4},{"id":165,"text":"to prove to all of us","depth":5},{"id":166,"text":"that he could be the independent , fair attorney general","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"America needs right now .","depth":6},{"id":168,"text":"He failed , \"","depth":3},{"id":169,"text":"said Kristine Lucius , a vice president at the Leadership Conference on Civil and Human Rights .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":339,"left":333,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":333,"left":241,"right":332,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":195,"right":240,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":195,"left":175,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare